      "text": "Harabaye umuserebanyi, ukaba wari umuhigi. Umusi umwe, urahiga umusi wose ariko ntihagira ico ufata.",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/vianneymanirambona2%40gmail.com%2f705de33b-4747-4d4c-9ce0-a09fd82d9170%2fThe+Lizard+and+the+Hyena%2faudio%2fd8d231ff-3dcd-4e1d-9bac-ddd5b607518e.mp3",
