      "text": "Ntibitevye, wa muserebanyi ufata ubunyegeri uca utangura kuburya. Uraburya gushika naho uhaga",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/vianneymanirambona2%40gmail.com%2f705de33b-4747-4d4c-9ce0-a09fd82d9170%2fThe+Lizard+and+the+Hyena%2faudio%2fi441e9321-ebbd-4445-a2a2-00ee77767be6.mp3",
