      "text": "Wa muserebanyi wumva iciyumviro kiraje. Uca ufata ningoga inkoni ndende utangura kwijiginyura.",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/vianneymanirambona2%40gmail.com%2f705de33b-4747-4d4c-9ce0-a09fd82d9170%2fThe+Lizard+and+the+Hyena%2faudio%2fi9a09259b-addf-4523-9e82-9587240eae48.mp3",
          "dur": 7.8366
