      "text": "Ya mfyisi ibonye wa mu serebanyi iwubaza iti: \"Mushinganta, wariye iki kugira urinde wihaganyuza ikintu kingana uko kwose?",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/vianneymanirambona2%40gmail.com%2f705de33b-4747-4d4c-9ce0-a09fd82d9170%2fThe+Lizard+and+the+Hyena%2faudio%2fi70c96b48-436b-4d4a-bd40-15efabbd295b.mp3",
