      "text": "Wa muserebanyi urayishura uti: \"Nariko ndarya inyama z'imfyisi zokeje, none rero mbonye uje, niko kwihaganyura kugira ndye iziwawe zo zikiri nshasha§",
      "audio": [
        {
          "src": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/vianneymanirambona2%40gmail.com%2f705de33b-4747-4d4c-9ce0-a09fd82d9170%2fThe+Lizard+and+the+Hyena%2faudio%2fi90a747cd-ec93-441b-9614-567d89d0b052.mp3",
